;*    This module implements encoder/decoder for quoted-printable as   */
;*    defined by the RFC 2045:                                         */
;*      Multipurpose Internet Mail Extensions                          */
;*      (MIME) Part One:                                               */
;*      Format of Internet Message Bodies                              */
;*    RFC 2045, may be found at:                                       */
